00:49:45,900 --> 00:49:49,480
 malo više prema tome dati pažnje,

466
00:49:49,480 --> 00:49:51,960
 jer, evo, zaključili smo sad

467
00:49:51,960 --> 00:49:53,960
 koliko ima tu problema,

468
00:49:53,960 --> 00:49:55,340
 koliko je intenzivno to

469
00:49:55,340 --> 00:49:58,160
 i baš to razdoblje mladih ljudi

470
00:49:58,160 --> 00:49:59,180
 koji se uključuju,

471
00:49:59,180 --> 00:50:01,520
 ali intenzivan je sam po sebi.

472
00:50:01,520 --> 00:50:02,580
 To su te emocije,

473
00:50:02,580 --> 00:50:03,520
 to je taj doživlje,

474
00:50:03,520 --> 00:50:04,520
 to je adrenalin,

475
00:50:04,520 --> 00:50:06,400
 to je, znači,

476
00:50:06,400 --> 00:50:08,360
 tu bi se svi skupa malo trebali više

477
00:50:08,360 --> 00:50:11,560
 skoncentrirati i doprinjeti

478
00:50:11,560 --> 00:50:12,380
 u tom dijelu.

479
00:50:12,380 --> 00:50:14,560
 Poruka.

480
00:50:14,560 --> 00:50:17,800
 Ne bi sad htio dužiti,

481
00:50:17,800 --> 00:50:20,400
 nego jednostavno sve znamo.

482
00:50:20,400 --> 00:50:24,580
 Znamo ko je istina put i život

483
00:50:24,580 --> 00:50:26,840
 staviti to ispred sebe

484
00:50:26,840 --> 00:50:29,360
 i onda nekako se sve skupa slaže.

485
00:50:29,360 --> 00:50:31,740
 Svakako ne sami,

486
00:50:31,740 --> 00:50:32,500
 nego zajedno.

487
00:50:32,500 --> 00:50:33,800
 Tako je, evo.

488
00:50:33,800 --> 00:50:36,420
 Ne bih to bolje sročila,

489
00:50:36,420 --> 00:50:38,460
 pa neću ni pokušavati.

490
00:50:38,460 --> 00:50:40,400
 Ovime ćemo zaključiti

491
00:50:40,400 --> 00:50:42,400
 današnju emisiju

492
00:50:42,400 --> 00:50:44,460
 Franjena ekonomija.

493
00:50:44,460 --> 00:50:45,820
 Dragi slušatelji,

494
00:50:45,820 --> 00:50:47,020
 hvala što ste bili s nama.

495
00:50:47,020 --> 00:50:48,740
 Dragi Leonard,

496
00:50:48,740 --> 00:50:50,540
 hvala vam na gostovanju.

497
00:50:50,540 --> 00:50:53,920
 I družimo se opet

498
00:50:53,920 --> 00:50:56,300
 u idućoj epizodi,

499
00:50:56,300 --> 00:50:58,800
 gdje ćemo nastaviti razgovarati

500
00:50:58,800 --> 00:51:01,040
 o sportu i ekonomiji.

501
00:51:01,040 --> 00:51:03,580
 S vama je bila Iva Kraljević,

502
00:51:03,580 --> 00:51:05,480
 a u tehnici s nama danas

503
00:51:05,480 --> 00:51:06,660
 Josip Dandić.

504
00:51:16,180 --> 00:51:28,060
 Od svih žena ti si ta,

505
00:51:28,060 --> 00:51:35,060
