506
00:51:35,060 --> 00:51:40,880
 mariju, puna milosti.

507
00:51:40,880 --> 00:51:49,240
 Od svih žena ti si ta,

508
00:51:49,240 --> 00:51:56,140
 koja hran je spasca postala,

509
00:51:56,140 --> 00:52:02,960
